data.description: Come and see this charming newly updated home in the heart of Foley. This Three Bedroom Two Bath house features a split floor plan, and has been recently updated with new paint, new vinyl plank flooring, the A/C unit is a 2021 and the roof was replaced in 2020-2021. The Primary bedroom features his and her closets for closet space and has double vanities in the bathroom. This home also features a two car garage for storage or workshop, a fireplace, SS appliances, and a fenced in backyard for privacy. The location is great being close to the Foley Hospital, OWA, Highway 59, the Baldwin Beach Express and nearby beaches. Alabama Right of Redemption may apply until 4/27/2024.
